Package: ergo-node-rust
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6
Suggests: fail2ban
Conflicts: ergo-proxy-node
Replaces: ergo-proxy-node
Maintainer: Muad'Dib <dev@blockhost.io>
Description: Ergo blockchain full node in Rust
 Ground-up Rust implementation of the Ergo blockchain node.
 Validates headers and blocks against mainnet consensus, maintains
 a persistent UTXO state (AVL+ tree), bootstraps via UTXO snapshot
 sync, runs a mempool, exposes a REST API, and supports mining.
